Link to video: https://github.com/aniskoubaa/ros_essentials_cpp/tree/master/src/topic03_perception/video 

To perform ball tracking in real time: 
1. Start the picamera driver- $ rosrun usb_cam usb_cam_node _pixel_format:=yuyv
2. Execute tennis_ball_picam_tracker.py 

Ball tracking on a recorded video: 
a) With ROS
1. Execute tennis_ball_publisher.py
2. Execute tennis_ball_subscriber.py
b) Without ROS
1. Execute ball_tracking video.py
